Changed ProxyPass example in docs from /lisp to /hunchentoot	

Version 0.6.1
2007-01-24
Reset to "faithful" external format on each iteration (bug caught by Viljo Marrandi and Ury Marshak)

Version 0.6.0
2007-01-23
